RAD_LOVS.LOV_QUERY: SELECT AC_GL_NO, AC_GL_DESC, AC_GL_CCY, IBAN_AC_NO, BRANCH_CODE, AC_OR_GL, GL_CATEGORY FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT WHERE AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND ('Y', 'Y') = (SELECT NVL(A.PARAM_VALUE, 'N'), NVL(B.PARAM_VALUE, 'N') FROM OLTBS_LOAN_PARAM_DETAIL A, OLTBS_LOAN_PARAM_DETAIL B WHERE A.PARAM_NAME = 'ALLOW_ALL_ACC_IN_OSI' AND B.PARAM_NAME = 'ALLOW_ALL_GL_ACC_IN_OSI') UNION SELECT /*+ PARALLEL(A,4) */ A.AC_GL_NO, A.AC_GL_DESC, A.AC_GL_CCY, A.IBAN_AC_NO, A.BRANCH_CODE, A.AC_OR_GL, A.GL_CATEGORY FROM OLTBS_ACCOUNT A WHERE AC_GL_REC_STATUS = 'O' AND AC_OR_GL = 'G' AND ('Y', 'Y') <> (SELECT NVL(A.PARAM_VALUE, 'N'), NVL(B.PARAM_VALUE, 'N') FROM OLTBS_LOAN_PARAM_DETAIL A, OLTBS_LOAN_PARAM_DETAIL B WHERE A.PARAM_NAME = 'ALLOW_ALL_ACC_IN_OSI' AND B.PARAM_NAME = 'ALLOW_ALL_GL_ACC_IN_OSI') ORDER BY AC_GL_NO
